messages.messageBody:
I love the digest today!
Food and music...no better topics (other than art).
I have Nanci's love for food and Meghans eclectic musical tastes I believe.
A food vacation? YES! My kind of trip.

I love Bowie, Yes, Creed, Dave Matthews, Enya, Sara McCloughin, Journey,
etc.....Plus all the Beethoven, Bach, Mozart, Debussy, etc.... and Opera. My
kids have Phantom of the Opera practically memorized!
blah, blah, blah.
I love it all.
The only country I like are some occasional "cross over" songs and the twangy
Dwight Yoakam.
Reggae is great fun too. Especially late at night down at the boardwalk at
Pensacola beach!!

Ren
